{"id":41722,"title":"102 | 第六模块课程介绍","content":"<h1>课件及源码地址</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://gitee.com/geektime-geekbang/eureka_lab\">https://gitee.com/geektime-geekbang/eureka_lab</a></p>\n","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":276100,"user_name":"马文龙","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1068432,"ip_address":"","ucode":"679B0F0AB402C7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/4d/90/25b6f544.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1611795172,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":100288,"content":"Eureka的实例数一般采用3&#47;5&#47;7&#47;9这样的奇数方式部署，类似ZK，保证集群中始终有一个多数(majority)可以做决策即可。具体的数量，没有经验值，主要看你的单个实例的机器&#47;网络的性能，然后需要通过监控数据才能确定。建议从小集群开始，根据监控数据再不断调优扩容。\n\n多IDC其实就是多Zone部署，Netflix Eureka主要面向AWS云部署的，AWS云中一个IDC对应一个Zone，Zone相当于同城的IDC，还有一个Region相当于异地的概念，一个Region中可以有多个Zone。所以，要理解Eureka的多IDC部署，弄清楚它的Zone&#47;Region的配置就可以了，可以看Netflix eureka的github上文档，或者spring cloud的文档。另外网上有不少演示样例，照着做一遍，应该可以理解，然后再根据你的具体IDC情况进行部署。参考样例：\nhttps:&#47;&#47;www.cnblogs.com&#47;idoljames&#47;p&#47;11620616.html\nhttps:&#47;&#47;blog.csdn.net&#47;chengqiuming&#47;article&#47;details&#47;102789277\n\n\n\n","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1611850715,"ip_address":"","comment_id":276100,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100007001,"comment_content":"杨老师，生产上服务上百个或上千的微服务模块的话，eureka的实例数多少为最优，还有它的多IDC架构是什么样的 ，能开一篇文章介绍一下吗","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":514599,"discussion_content":"Eureka的实例数一般采用3/5/7/9这样的奇数方式部署，类似ZK，保证集群中始终有一个多数(majority)可以做决策即可。具体的数量，没有经验值，主要看你的单个实例的机器/网络的性能，然后需要通过监控数据才能确定。建议从小集群开始，根据监控数据再不断调优扩容。\n\n多IDC其实就是多Zone部署，Netflix Eureka主要面向AWS云部署的，AWS云中一个IDC对应一个Zone，Zone相当于同城的IDC，还有一个Region相当于异地的概念，一个Region中可以有多个Zone。所以，要理解Eureka的多IDC部署，弄清楚它的Zone/Region的配置就可以了，可以看Netflix eureka的github上文档，或者spring cloud的文档。另外网上有不少演示样例，照着做一遍，应该可以理解，然后再根据你的具体IDC情况进行部署。参考样例：\nhttps://www.cnblogs.com/idoljames/p/11620616.html\nhttps://blog.csdn.net/chengqiuming/article/details/102789277\n\n\n\n","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1611850715,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":62349,"user_name":"亚林","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1018972,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4A5A6D24314B79","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/8c/5c/3f164f66.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1548036350,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":22084,"content":"加油！","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1548072010,"ip_address":"","comment_id":62349,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100007001,"comment_content":"我也看到这里了","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":437178,"discussion_content":"加油！","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1548072010,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":45627,"user_name":"Luke","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1093041,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1163BC279235A5","user_header":"https